description:
Adhesive Label Release
Finally you can move and replace shelf labels with no sticky residue!!
No more scraping off the old label!
    The old label just peels off. Label Release is easy to use, just apply to the front of your shelving. These strips have a base of adhesive vinyl to be used on flat face shelving. Remove backing and apply to front of flat edge of shelves or leave backing on and snap into "C" Channel Molding. Cut rolls to any length you need. Use with any label and remove it without any residue or scraping.
*1 3/16" x 200' Roll.
